  "notes": [
    "This study demonstrates a novel mechanism where PSMD14 acts as a deubiquitinating enzyme that stabilizes HMMR protein through K63-linked deubiquitination",
    "The dual activation of both TGF-\u03b2/Smad and PI3K/AKT/mTOR pathways by PSMD14 represents a unique finding in lung adenocarcinoma",
    "Combination therapy with PSMD14 inhibitor Capzimin and TGF-\u03b2 inhibitor galunisertib shows enhanced therapeutic efficacy"
